T-11: User Notifications
Users receive notifications about orders, messages, approvals, and updates. They can see unread counts, mark notifications as read, delete them, and open related pages.

T-12: Wishlist
Users can add books to their wishlist and remove them anytime. The wishlist helps users remember books they want to buy later.

T-13: Edit Profile
Users can update their name, email, and profile picture. After saving, the system shows a success message.

T-14: Change Password
Users can change their password by entering the current and new password. The system checks correctness and confirms the change.

T-15: Add Review
Users can give star ratings and write reviews for books. A message is shown after submitting the review.
